{"type": "article", "id": 8995, "title": "Other Stories & Vans 联名鞋款", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-29T07:33:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235015sou6WXIr2Sxp9UZd.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t昨天我们看了匡威更新版的 Slip-On，今天来看看 Other Stories 和 Vans 联名推出的三个春夏鞋款，两款 Slip-On 分别是经典驼色和白底黑点，而其经典 Old Skool 则选择了柔和的驼色，看上去帅气中带着甜美。此外，他们还邀请了 86 岁的超模 Daphne Selfe 拍摄广告大片，为品牌注入了另一番个性和气质。这是<a href=\"http://www.stories.com/se/Co-Labs/Vans_Other_Stories\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235013fxDtS9n1abqA7O0K.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235014OWAp8wmM5antbJHR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235014E2VthzUqTpjWbcgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235015Y0Bjf9Qn5arDdGoF.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.4046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}